    "body": "Here are the first steps to make sure you have the funds.\r\n- Download [Geth 1.9](https://geth.ethereum.org/downloads/)\r\n- Do light sync `geth --syncmode=light console`\r\n- Wait until it syncs\r\n- In the console write `eth.accounts`. It gives you the local accounts.\r\n- Execute `eth.getBalance(<your account>)`\r\n\r\nThis should ensure that your have a synced node and see your funds. We can go from there.",
